be a dear and have a seat?

00:14:17.610 --> 00:14:19.530
So, what's up. The usual?

00:14:19.610 --> 00:14:21.450
Yeah, Dad's in a mood.

00:14:21.530 --> 00:14:24.990
[UZAKI] Ugh. I knew I should
have kept my big mouth shut.

00:14:25.070 --> 00:14:26.280
[FUJIO]
Now that we're all here,

00:14:26.370 --> 00:14:29.040
the Uzaki family meeting
shall commence.

