have dinner already, Ma?

00:15:01.650 --> 00:15:03.570
Hana's technically an adult,
so wouldn't it make

00:15:03.650 --> 00:15:05.780
more sense to let her do
whatever she wants now?

00:15:05.860 --> 00:15:07.570
Not gonna lie, Daddy,
it's real wack for you

00:15:07.660 --> 00:15:09.250
to try and decide
things for her.

