children like this,

00:15:11.330 --> 00:15:13.750
then they'll only end up
resenting you once they grow up.

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:17.080
Why do you kids always
pick on your old man?

00:15:17.170 --> 00:15:18.710
I can't believe it
was only yesterday

00:15:18.790 --> 00:15:20.130
when you were still in diapers.

