These are the sorts of things
your old man is worried about,

00:17:24.340 --> 00:17:27.050
ya know. Does he have
a good personality?

00:17:27.130 --> 00:17:28.880
Does he have good manners?

00:17:28.970 --> 00:17:30.560
Does he take care of
his mental health?

00:17:30.630 --> 00:17:33.930
